Where do all the clusters map in M2?

Load libraries.

library(Seurat)
library(tidyverse)
library(RColorBrewer)

Load umap of cluster.

load("/Volumes/Bud_SSD/20210505-seurat/fin-integr-clust-6/fin-M2-clust-3/fin-M2_1-clust-2/umap-by-cluster-fin-M2_1-clust-2.Robj")
m2.1.umap <- subclust.umap
m2.1.umap$mutant.subclust <- as.character(m2.1.umap$mutant.subclust)
head(m2.1.umap)
table(m2.1.umap$mutant.subclust)

M2.1.1 M2.1.2 
  3369    889

Load umap of subclusters.

load("/Volumes/Bud_SSD/20210505-seurat/fin-integr-clust-6/fin-M2-clust-3/fin-M2_1-clust-2/fin-M2_1_1-clust-3/umap-by-cluster-fin-M2_1_1-clust-3.Robj")
m2.1.1.umap <- sub.subclust.umap
table(m2.1.1.umap$mutant.sub.subclust)

M2.1.1.1 M2.1.1.2 M2.1.1.3 
    1782      980      607

Recode M2 cluster into subclusters.

m2.1.umap[as.vector(rownames(m2.1.1.umap %>% filter(mutant.sub.subclust == "M2.1.1.1"))), "mutant.subclust"] <- "M2.1.1.1"
m2.1.umap[as.vector(rownames(m2.1.1.umap %>% filter(mutant.sub.subclust == "M2.1.1.2"))), "mutant.subclust"] <- "M2.1.1.2"
m2.1.umap[as.vector(rownames(m2.1.1.umap %>% filter(mutant.sub.subclust == "M2.1.1.3"))), "mutant.subclust"] <- "M2.1.1.3"
m2.1.umap$mutant.subclust <- factor(m2.1.umap$mutant.subclust, levels = c("M2.1.1.1", "M2.1.1.2", "M2.1.1.3", "M2.1.2"))
table(m2.1.umap$mutant.subclust)

M2.1.1.1 M2.1.1.2 M2.1.1.3   M2.1.2 
    1782      980      607      889 
subclust.umap <- m2.1.umap
save(subclust.umap, file = "/Volumes/Bud_SSD/20210505-seurat/fin-integr-clust-6/fin-M2-clust-3/fin-M2_1-clust-2/umap-by-cluster-fin-M2_1-clust-2-4.Robj")

Generate label umap.

umap.label <- subclust.umap %>% group_by(mutant.subclust) %>% summarize(umap.1 = median(umap.1), umap.2 = median(umap.2))

Generate cluster umap.

cluster.umap <- ggplot() +
geom_point(data = sample(subclust.umap), mapping = aes(x = umap.1, y = umap.2, color = mutant.subclust), size = 0.1) +
geom_text(data = umap.label, mapping = aes(x = umap.1, y = umap.2, label = mutant.subclust), size = 3.5) +
labs(title = "M2.1, Nipbl Flox/+", x = "UMAP 1", y = "UMAP 2", color = "Cluster") +
  guides(color = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 2.3))) +
theme_classic(base_size = 7) +
theme(axis.line = element_blank(), axis.ticks = element_blank(), axis.text = element_blank(), plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 7), legend.key.size = unit(7, "pt"))
cluster.umap

ggsave(plot = cluster.umap, filename = "/Volumes/Bud_SSD/20210505-seurat/fin-integr-clust-6/fin-M2-clust-3/fin-M2_1-clust-2/umap-by-cluster-fin-M2_1-clust-2-4.png", device = "png", width = 6.5, height = 4.5, units = "in")
